Data Binding
---------------------
1. One way Binding  - one dimensional binding
                    - communication between data
                    - ts->html , html->ts

    methods
    -------------
    1.1 Component to view binding - ts->html
        component-ts
        view-html
        1.1.1 string interpollation - {{data}}
        - display data in html file directly
        - where ever  we want to disply data put datastoring variable name inside {{}} backet
        1.1.2 property binding - [propertyName]="data"
        - display data 

    1.2 View to component Binding - html->ts
        1.2.1 event binding -(eventName)="methodname()"
        1.2.2 $event binding-(eventname)="methodName($event)
            -event nadakkunna time data access cheyyam. passes an angument when calling method().
        1.2.3 Event Binding using templete rendering variable - #datavariable
        html->html data trasferring
2.Two way binding
---------------------------
html->ts ts->html
    2.1 NgModel -[(ngModel)]="variable"
                - changing data in ts and html automatically
                - data changing in html at the same time data change in their corresponding ts file
                - To get NgModel  we wa.nt to import an external module called formsmodule
                - ids and name should be unique when using 2 way bindingng


Api call in angular
-----------------------------
HttpClient is a class

HttpClientModule  is a module.HttpClient inside this module.HttpClient contains post,put,get,patch,delete

HttpClientModule-HttpClient-post,put,get,patch,delete
